msgid "🎯 Introduction"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:27
msgid ""
"**pyMediaManager (pyMM)** is a portable, Python-based media management "
"application designed for photographers, videographers, and digital "
"content creators who need a flexible, portable solution for managing "
"media projects across multiple storage devices."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:29
msgid "Key Benefits"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:31
msgid ""
"**✨ Truly Portable**: Run from any drive (USB, external HDD, network) "
"without installation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:32
msgid ""
"**🎨 Modern UI**: Beautiful Fluent Design interface powered by PySide6 and"
" QFluentWidgets"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:33
msgid ""
"**🔌 Plugin System**: Extensible architecture supporting DigiKam, "
"ExifTool, FFmpeg, and more"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:34
msgid "**📦 Project-Based**: Organize media into self-contained portable projects"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:35
msgid ""
"**🔒 Secure**: No system modifications, registry changes, or "
"administrative privileges required"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:36
msgid "**🚀 Fast**: Native Python 3.13 performance with async operations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:38
msgid "Use Cases"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:40
msgid "**Photographers**: Manage photo collections with DigiKam integration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:41
msgid "**Videographers**: Organize video projects with FFmpeg processing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:42
msgid "**Backup Solutions**: Maintain portable media archives across devices"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:43
msgid ""
"**Multi-Site Workflows**: Sync projects between office, home, and field "
"locations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-guide.md:44
msgid "**Education**: Portable labs for teaching media management workflows"
msgstr ""

